snippet.title: Stellar Interface Trailer
snippet.description:
Stellar Interface is a rogue-lite, shmup filled with content to unlock and maps to explore, everything is randomly generated so you will never have two different runs! The game has 8 crazy bosses full of pop culture references, a synergistic perk system with more than 100 perks to choose and an endless mode to test out your skills.

The game is available on Steam, Xbox, and on Nintendo Switch!

You can play it right now on:
Steam:  https://store.steampowered.com/app/517330/Stellar_Interface/
Xbox: https://www.microsoft.com/store/apps/9P7WRZWT294V
Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/stellar-interface-switch/

For more news and updates, follow us on:
